     Chem. Phys. 2009 356(1-3), 98-109
     doi.org/10.1016/j.chemphys.2008.10.036
  3. Caldeweyher, E.; Bannwarth, C.; Grimme, S.
     Extension of the D3 dispersion coefficient model
     J. Chem. Phys. 2017 147 , 034112
     doi.org/10.1063/1.4993215
  4. Caldeweyher, E.; Ehlert, S.; Hansen, A.; Neugebauer, H.; Spicher, S.; Bannwarth, C.; Grimme, S.
     A generally applicable atomic-charge dependent London dispersion correction
     J. Chem. Phys. 2019 150 , 154122
     doi.org/10.1063/1.5090222
